### 🧍 Registrera en ny användare
POST http://localhost:3000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

### 🔐 Logga in och hämta token
POST http://localhost:3000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testuser",
  "password": "test123"
}


### 🧾 Skapa en ny film (Endast admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "The Matrix",
  "director": ["The Wachowskis"],
  "releaseYear": 1999,
  "genre": ["Sci-Fi", "Action"]
}

### ✏️ Uppdatera film (Endast admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/<MOVIE_ID>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "The Matrix Reloaded"
}

### 🗑️ Ta bort film och relaterade recensioner (Endast admin)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/<MOVIE_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>


### 📝 Skapa en recension för en film
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

{
  "movieId": "<MOVIE_ID>",
  "rating": 8,
  "comment": "Grym film!"
}

### ✏️ Uppdatera en recension (endast om ägare)
PUT http://localhost:3000/reviews/<REVIEW_ID>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

{
  "rating": 9,
  "comment": "Ännu bättre andra gången."
}

### 🗑️ Ta bort en recension (endast om ägare)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/reviews/<REVIEW_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>


### 📄 Hämta information om inloggad användare
GET http://localhost:3000/user
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 📄 Hämta alla recensioner från inloggad användare
GET http://localhost:3000/user/review
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 🔍 Hämta användarnamn via userId
GET http://localhost:3000/user/<USER_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### ❌ Radera inloggad användare och alla deras recensioner
DELETE http://localhost:3000/user
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>


### 🎬 Hämta alla filmer
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

### 🎬 Hämta detaljer om en specifik film
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/<MOVIE_ID>

### 💬 Hämta alla recensioner för en specifik film
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/<MOVIE_ID>/reviews


### 🧾 Hämta alla recensioner (Endast admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

### 🔍 Hämta specifik recension via ID
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/<REVIEW_ID>
